text.tspan: Name: ZENZO
Age: 30
Status: Detained
Role: Ex-Staff
Documentation:
Click this to exit
Doctor Zenzo was a formidable force
in the realm of science. Especially
here with us. He decided one day to
use his own machine on himself, due
to (according to him) the fact that his
genes don't allow him to die. We are
still not sure what he was doing about
that but it drove him crazy. He started
becoming something inhuman, he had
become an amalgam. With the last shred
of sentience he had left, he inserted a
chip into his brain, and locked himself
inside of one of our indestructible
chambers. We have yet to see Zenzo.
DONK
Industries
